<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The basic plot is about an Israeli group of spies, lead by Kurtz and Gadi Becker, aka Joseph, who recruits Charlie to infiltrate a group of Palestinia<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">‚Ä¶more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The basic plot is about an Israeli group of spies, lead by Kurtz and Gadi Becker, aka Joseph, who recruits Charlie to infiltrate a group of Palestinian terrorists. There is obviously a whole lot more to the 400+ page book, but that is the general gist of it.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
