        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780553239812" href="/book/show/606871.Little_Drummer_Girl">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/29539853-selina-kyle?shelf=favorite-characters">favorite-characters</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/29539853-selina-kyle?shelf=real-life-in-fiction">real-life-in-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/29539853-selina-kyle?shelf=espionage">espionage</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/29539853-selina-kyle?shelf=military">military</a>, 
